<includeonly>{{#invoke:GameData|recipe}}</includeonly><noinclude>

==Usage==
<nowiki>{{Recipe|Item|Structure|Quantity}}</nowiki>

Item parameter doesn't need to be defined in most cases, as it defaults to page name.

Likewise for Quantity parameter, as the product is rarely above 1.

Implemented in [[Module:GameData]], which reads the data page directly.

===Examples===
<nowiki>{{Recipe|Blood Essence|Blood Press|10}}</nowiki>
{{Recipe|Blood Essence|Blood Press|10}}
<nowiki>{{Recipe|Vermin Salve|Crafting}}</nowiki>
{{Recipe|Vermin Salve|Crafting}}

==Data==
Data is stored on [[Template:Recipe/data]].
